reviews.review_text: Famous Warfield Shows Show from 1980, not 1989.  Part of the famous 3-set series with first set being acoustic.  Some selected for "Reckoning" LP.  Nice high quality soundboard!

1980, not 1989 This threw me for a loop for a minute when it came up on my Time Machine as October 7, 1989. Its actually from October 7, 1980 and a very clean, beautifully mixed example of the epic arun of acoustic shows that happened in October 1980. I don't see this period referred to as such, but to my ear it was one of maybe three maybe four high water marks for the band. Such beautiful music!
